title: Delay closing the receiver app on the Pebble.
message:
Delay closing the receiver app on the Pebble.

Recent versions of the firmware seem to have a race where a closing app message look like it's discarded. Thus we introduce a small delay before sending the actual message after receiving the battery reading.

title: Finally sort out how to force f*cking Pebble app to install our bundle
message: Finally sort out how to force f*cking Pebble app to install our bundle

title: [watchapp] Build a real watch app UI.
message:
[watchapp] Build a real watch app UI.

Beta 6 seems to have increased latency in sending data which means we don't have time to receive battery value before the app kills itself. Add an interface so that we can have more time and also show the user something if he selects the watchapp directly.
